 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003ECovertix equips enterprise organizations with iron-clad independent\nfile-level surveillance and control, protecting sensitive data, inside and\noutside the organization.  The company\u00e2\u20ac\u2122s turnkey, flagship product,\nSmartCipher\u00e2\u201e\u00a2 dynamically tags digital assets according to file context and\ncontent; automatically and continuously tracking and securing these assets.\nThe hallmark of SmartCipher\u0026#8217;s unique capabilities is T3Security \u00e2\u20ac\u201c Total\nSecurity \u00e2\u20ac\u201c safeguard any file, anytime, anywhere; Targeted Protection \u00e2\u20ac\u201c\nautomatic tagging of the most sensitive digital assets; and Transparent\nImplementation \u00e2\u20ac\u201c zero workflow interruption to users.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ESmartCipher\u00e2\u201e\u00a2 has been installed in a variety of public and private\ntier-one enterprise customers.  Committed to developing pioneering IRM solutions, the Covertix team has accumulated extensive experience and\nexpertise in the disciplines of Information Rights Management and IT Security, allowing for unparalleled security and ease of use. Headquartered\nin Even Yehuda, Israel, Covertix is a privately held company.\u003C/p\u003E",
